    Shapiro-Wilk test data

    shapiro_reference.Rd

    A dataset with 11 values of men weights expressed in pounds. The dataset is provided for testing the results of fct_shapiro.

    shapirotest_reference

    Format

    a vector with 11 numerical elements.

    Source

    An analysis of variance test for normality (complete samples), Biometrika (1965), 52, 3 and 2, p. 591. Section 4 - Examples, pag. 606, Example 1. http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0006-3444%28196512%2952%3A3%2F4%3C591%3AAAOVTF%3E2.0.CO%3B2-B.

    Author

    S. S. Shapiro

    M. B. Wilk
